### Список рейсов
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/fights
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "from_airport": "country + name",
    "to_airport": "country + name",
    "date": "datetime",
    "price": "number"
  }
]

### Информация о пользователе
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me/
X-User-Name: {{username}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tickets": [
    {
      "ticket_uid": "uuid",
      "flight_number": "string",
      "from_airport": "country + name",
      "to_airport": "country + name",
      "date": "datetime",
      "price": "number"
    }
  ],
  "privilege": {
    "balance": "number",
    "status": "string"
  }
}

