### Вернуть билет
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tickets/{{ticketUid}}
X-User-Name: {{username}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Получить историю бонусного счета
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/privilege
X-User-Name: {{username}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "balance": "number",
  "status": "string",
  "history": [
    {
      "date": "datetime",
      "balance_diff": "number",
      "operation_type": "string"
    }
  ]
}